input_str: After recently re-examining thrash metal's "Big Four," I began to think back on a lot of the other bands that fans of the genre were listening to back in the 1980s. Metallica, Slayer, Anthrax, and Megadeth got a lot of attention, they were far from the only popular bands playing fast and aggressive metal.
